#. Tag: para
#: utime.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the geographic location to <quote>Greenwich, England</quote> using the "
"<guilabel>Set Location</guilabel> window (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>G</keycap></keycombo>). Note that the Local Time (<abbrev>LT</"
"abbrev>) and the Universal Time (<abbrev>UT</abbrev>) are now the same."
msgstr ""
"Defina a localización xeográfica como <quote>Greenwich, Inglaterra</quote> "
"usando a xanela <guilabel>Definir a localización</guilabel> (<keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>G</keycap></keycombo>). A hora local "
"(<abbrev>LT</abbrev>) e a hora universal (<abbrev>UT</abbrev>) pasarán a ser "
"a mesma."

